data.description: Looking for one level open concept living on a corner lot in a convenient city location? Well look no further this is the one! This updated brick ranch was updated about 3 yrs ago. Updates included new roof, new kitchen appliances, new kitchen counter tops, new light fixtures, new paint inside and out! From the moment you walk in the front door you will realize how spacious and well laid out this house is! The large living area features a stunning brick fire place with gas logs.  The modern kitchen design has plenty of cabinet and counter top space especially with the large snack bar area. The kitchen opens up to a huge dining area perfect for entertaining! This home features beautiful bamboo  wood flooring in all the main living areas then in the bedrooms and bathrooms you will find durable wood laminate flooring. There is a primary bedroom with a  primary bathroom. This house also has two other nice sized bedrooms and a large hall bathroom.  Off from the kitchen you will find a nice mudroom with washer and dryer hook up, a utility sink and plenty of cabinets and shelves for storage. There is a one car attached garage. Out back you will find a fully fenced beautiful back yard along with a large storage building for extra storage! You definitely will want to make plans to come see this one! The seller is giving a $2500 shower allowance for the replacement of the shower in the primary bathroom which has a crack in the shower pan payable at closing. Curtains in living room do not convey.  There are two cats in the home please be careful and do not let them outside while looking at the house. The seller is a relative of the agent. All information contained herein is deemed reliable but is subject to buyers verification.
